text: Wellmann is a German surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Allan Wellmann (born 1954), Guatemalan footballer *Dieter Wellmann (born 1942), German fencer *Ellen Wellmann (born 1948), German middle and long-distance runner *Ernst Wellmann (1904–1970), German Wehrmacht officer *Paul-Heinz Wellmann (born 1952), West German middle-distance runner ==See also== *Wellman (disambiguation) Category:German-language surnames
title: Wellmann
